Kizz Daniel announced via his Instagram page that his album “No Bad Songz” will be released on the 30th of November.
The album includes international artists like  Wretch 32, Diplo, Diamond Platnumz and Sarkodie. “No Bad Song” will be released under Flyboy Inc.   A post shared by Kizz Daniel (@iamkizzdaniel) on Jul 27, 2018 at 2:07am PDT   “No Bad Songz” drops 30th Nov  ____ #nbsthealbum FLYBOYINC 4L  ___ Glory be to God A post shared by  Kizz Daniel (@iamkizzdaniel) on Nov 9, 2018 at 12:14am PST